OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPatchy cloud at first this
OL,6,Fmorning, but this breaking and
OL,7,Fclearing to give plenty of strong
OL,8,Fsunshine across the region. Feeling
OL,9,Fvery hot and humid with light winds
OL,10,Fthrough the afternoon, a touch fresher
OL,11,Faround the coast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FStaying very warm into the
OL,14,Fevening with some late sunshine. A
OL,15,Fvery warm and muggy night to follow,
OL,16,Fperhaps with a few mist and fog
OL,17,Fpatches.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
