OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FVery hot and humid with
OL,6,Fstrong sunshine through the day. Light
OL,7,Fwinds and continuing to feel very warm
OL,8,Finto the evening.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,11,FExtremely hot and humid on Thursday,
OL,12,Fparticularly in the south. Strong
OL,13,Fsunshine at times, but increasingly
OL,14,Fcloudy by Thursday with showers
OL,15,Fpossible. Becoming slightly cooler
OL,16,Ffrom Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
